Grubb & Ellis Enters Agreement With C-III Capital, Colony

-- B y   K a r a   W e t z e l
-- 
2011-10-17T12:19:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/grubb-ellis-enters-agreement-with-c-iii-capital-colony.html
Grubb & Ellis Co. (GBE)  said C-III Capital
Partners LLC has agreed to invest $10 million into the company
and will become a “significant” stakeholder.  C-III has partnered with  Colony Capital LLC  for a
transaction and is exclusive negotiations with Grubb & Ellis,
the real estate services company said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kara Wetzel in New York at 
 kwetzel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
